 alt="" width="694" height="400" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.42-694x400.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.42-768x443.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.42.jpg 777w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>而上載了僅僅 3 小時，黃明志的歌曲就已經賣完，總共賺取了等值 85 萬美元的虛擬貨幣。黃明志的作品《玻璃心 Fragile》還有《飆高音》都有放上 NFT 售賣。黃明志表示，感謝大家用行動支持藝術創作者，他自己不會將這筆虛擬貨幣兌現，希望能永遠在虛擬世界裡流通，以對抗世界銀行。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.51.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070254" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.51-694x402.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="402" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.51-694x402.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.51-768x445.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.51.jpg 774w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_57233"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oa-bo2AUrCw?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p></p><div class="feedflare">
